{"tid":205685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(休班警) 稱查案致患精神病，警員偷拍罪成","createTime":"2017-04-18T03:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T11:46:45.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0196abb501d02b221d49bfe7d9ab890feec1e3","tid":205685,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"警員柯榮發（34歲）一日內在上班途中、午膳時及下班後，於港鐵站連環偷拍14名女子裙底，他早前承認14項有違公德罪，...........。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今透露精神醫生指被告患上適應性障礙症，裁判官判他200小時社會服務令，另付堂費5,000元。<br />\n<br />\n............辯方今指被告加入警隊8年，獲得上司嘉許14次，事業因今次犯案而毀於一旦，將會面臨被革職，據精神醫生意見，只要被告繼續接受治療，重犯機會低。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月12日被告在深水埗港鐵站A2出口電梯上偷拍22歲女學生裙底57秒，被途人發現及制服。警方在其手機再找到25段裙底影片，介乎1至44秒長，涉及另外13名女子，於同日在港鐵美孚站及金鐘站拍攝。"},{"pid":"86461674153045d020072ea620c176c5a573c9e7","tid":205685,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7be05a496a8ce18a6164a9f94f48ece0ab9da3","tid":205685,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"有精神病仲適唔適合做警<del>員</del>犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2b4da51620ffbdd3bb746504f8fbb9a9e8d7ca","tid":205685,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有精神病仲適唔適合做警<del>員</del>犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府唔會炒人架"},{"pid":"76beed39063416e9a17d0bd4ce374480de5c3926","tid":205685,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有精神病仲適唔適合做警<del>員</del>犬<img src=\"/assets/face